---
layout: layout.njk
title: Blog | Potloodgum - Webdesign Insights and Case Studies
description: Explore articles on accessible web design, case studies of non-profit projects, and insights on creating human-centered digital experiences.
keywords: accessible web design blog, human-centered design articles, non-profit web design case studies, web accessibility tips, social impact web design
pagination:
  data: collections.blog
  size: 10
  reverse: true
---
{% include "partials/_header.njk" %}

<main>
  <section class="blog-header radius-top-left radius-top-right">
    <h1>BLOG</h1>
    <p>Thoughts on accessible and human-centered web design</p>
  </section>

  <section class="blog-list radius-bottom-left radius-bottom-right">
    {% if collections.blog.length %}
      <div class="blog-grid">
        {% for post in pagination.items %}
          <article class="blog-card">
            <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
            <div class="blog-card-meta">
              <time datetime="{{ post.date | dateIso }}">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
              {% if post.data.tags %}
                <div class="tags">
                  {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
                    {% if tag != "blog" %}
                      <span class="tag">{{ tag }}</span>
                    {% endif %}
                  {% endfor %}
                </div>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
            <p class="blog-card-excerpt">{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
            <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="read-more">Read more</a>
          </article>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>

      {% if pagination.pages.length > 1 %}
        <nav class="pagination" aria-label="Blog pagination">
          <ul>
            {% if pagination.href.previous %}
              <li><a href="{{ pagination.href.previous }}" aria-label="Previous page">Previous</a></li>
            {% endif %}
            
            {% for pageUrl in pagination.hrefs %}
              <li>
                <a href="{{ pageUrl }}" {% if pagination.page.url == pageUrl %}aria-current="page"{% endif %}>
                  {{ loop.index }}
                </a>
              </li>
            {% endfor %}
            
            {% if pagination.href.next %}
              <li><a href="{{ pagination.href.next }}" aria-label="Next page">Next</a></li>
            {% endif %}
          </ul>
        </nav>
      {% endif %}
    {% else %}
      <p class="no-posts">Blog posts coming soon. Stay tuned!</p>
    {% endif %}
  </section>
</main>
